title: 820-4924 No post. Not cycling.
message: This board has all of the basic voltages but is not turning on. No sip signals. It has no pulse on 5V_S4. Has 3v3 on L7560. Has 3.3V on both sides of R1300/1/2/3. I've checked as much as I can think of. I've attached pre-ultrasonic pics. I've removed and resoldered all of the components in the spill area. I replaced U1900 and a few others that got hit harder just in case. Not sure where to go next.
